name: Chantal Aazam
description: I would be so happy to live my life with only you. I would never again need another man. Not as long as you are near my dearest one. This is the type of love I need to feel . Yes, this is the kind of love I wish to share with no-one else but you !!! I want to see your lovely face every day. Love awaits me on your lips. I need to trace love with my Love awaits pounding in my heart and my heart needs to be so close to yours. Yes, darling, this is the kind of love I wish to share only with you!!! I want to tell you, “I love you” and hear you say the same to me. I want you to have my new born and stay until I fade away unto heaven.
